'''Elboneno''' is a character in the [[Season 5|fifth season]]. He will be played by [[Peter Silverleaf]].<ref>[http://www.spotlight.com/6938-0161-0123/]</ref> Interestingly, the word "elboneno" spelled backwards is "one noble".
sections.In the books: In the ''[[A Song of Ice and Fire]]'' novels there is no mention of a character named Elboneno.
